<br>
But, in a group situation, so do wizards, really.  WE need an Enchanter and a Bard to get enough mana regen going to do consistent large amounts of damage.  Only with C2 and bardsong can I afford the mana to be productive on every single pull.  Otherwise, I have to pick and choose which monsters I will nuke.<br>
